## Legion Stats Pane

Whenever the stock character stats pane is shown, this WeakAura
overlays it with a re-creation of the pre-Legion detailed stats pane.

![Screenshot](./screenshot.jpg?raw=true)

**Classes**: All

**Requested by**: Arc
